import React from 'react';

import {
  Container,
  ServiceContainer,
  Title,
  FooterItem,
  InstitutionalContainer,
  SocialContainer,
  DownloadsContainer,
  LineContainer,
  ItemText,
} from './styles';

const Footer: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Wrapper>
        <ServiceContainer>
          <Title>Services</Title>
          <FooterItem>
            <ItemText />
          </FooterItem>
        </ServiceContainer>
        <InstitutionalContainer>
          <Title>Institutional</Title>
          <FooterItem>
            <ItemText />
          </FooterItem>
        </InstitutionalContainer>
        <SocialContainer>
          <Title>Social Networks</Title>
        </SocialContainer>
        <DownloadsContainer>
          <Title>Downloads</Title>
        </DownloadsContainer>
      </Wrapper>
      <LineContainer />
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Footer;
